<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>٢١٧- <span class="c1">"أيما إهاب دبغ فقد طهر"</span> ٤.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
